name: JIGOKU SHOUJU; a Hell within your head
description:
Celebrating my 1k followers on Twitter, here's for you a girl named Jigoku.
Originally from my mix-media painting back to 2017.

"Jelaga-jelaga yang berwujud Kenangan, riuh bergumul membentuk kembali Neraka"

"all the lampblack in the form of memories, noisily scrambling to reshape the hell"
